net.sf.oereader

Class OEFolderInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.oereader.OEBase
      • net.sf.oereader.OEIndexedInfo
        • net.sf.oereader.OEFolderInfo

  • public class OEFolderInfo
extends OEIndexedInfo
    Contains the information for a Folder object. This object is only used in the FolderDB .dbx files. The pointers to the FolderInfo objects are stored in the Tree.
